oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Reaction of (Z,Z)-cycloocta-1,5-diene under modified Woodward-Prevost conditions: A simple synthesis of functionalised cis-bicyclo[3.3.0]octanes
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: DEOTA, PT
SINGH, V
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: 1,5-cyclooctadiene
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The reaction of (Z,Z)-cycloocta-1,5-diene under modified Woodward-Prevost conditions (potassium iodate-iodine-potassium acetate in glacial acetic acid) results in the formation of functionalised bicyclic systems (3,4) and the cis diol 2; a plausible mechanism for their formation is described.
